{"tid":1754592,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[禁食人血饅頭]請當選區議員捐出少量薪津成立新抗爭基金","createTime":"2019-11-25T09:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T20:36:35.000Z","uid":15415,"like":44,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8e368760c97083f8ac99b99f40e657f3516b0483","tid":1754592,"uid":15415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:12:49.000Z","msg":"你地能夠當選，或多或少係食緊人血饅頭，食完做返少少野天公地道，已經無人期望你地肯上前線，以下係香港人好卑微既要求：<br />\n<br />\n請捐出部分薪津幫被捕人士，安家費又好打官司又好，求下你地大恩大德施捨下比義士，<span style=\"color: red;\">依家有成388席，每月$3k已經係講緊100萬一個月、1200萬一年</span>，再眾籌下一定大撚把人肯再捐錢，好簡單已經係半個612基金，唔洗你地班大帝用自己荷包比，求下你地用議員津貼幫下義士。<br />\n<br />\n最簡單係捐比星火，再唔係比你地班泛民捐比612都是但。<span style=\"color: red;\">但最好係成立一個新既抗爭基金</span>，有兩個好處：<br />\n<br />\n1）新既基金比起普通捐錢有更大個光環，有你地著數，幫你地長選長有，<span style=\"color: red;\">你地食得好好睇睇既話大家都想比機會你地繼續食人血饅頭</span>。<br />\n<br />\n2）我地需要一個更明顯係幫前線手足既基金，612基金不被信任、星火入唔到班和理非屋，有新既大型基金班前線唔洗下下驚做Condom，<span style=\"color: gold;\">新基金委任信托人我求下你地心胸廣闊d，接納所有派系參與，gphone、天琦、熱血、陳雲、泛民、李怡、陶傑、鄭立、渾水、SharonHom、各大學生會、telegram前線channel......</span>通通都可以考盧比佢地加入管理，每月$3k好撚少，求下你地唔好咁小家，<span style=\"color: orange;\">求下你地比班本土派加入管理，和勇真正合一，唔好浪費個議席，我地唔撚係選你出黎爭取加密巴士班次。</span>"},{"pid":"452882dc44d7cb16a8d0feab019312f812a7fcb0","tid":1754592,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:13:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">依家我哋區選贏咗，外國好關注我哋！<br />\n係咪連少少嘢都唔肯做呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n最新的tweets 一定響bot <br />\n總之<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> Retweet Like Reply </span></span>就得<br />\n㩒入👉 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=8e5c1745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task</span></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\nSen. Marco Rubio<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=2a3aec05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&h=2dc87735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928</a><br />\n<br />\nSen. Rick Scott<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1198739997911846913\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1198739997911846913&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=6e6129d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1198739997911846913&h=291b9b3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1198739997911846913</a><br />\n<br />\nSen. Marsha Blackburn<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1198773803976810496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1198773803976810496&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=0c19f8f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1198773803976810496&h=03c18e02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1198773803976810496</a><br />\n<br />\n更加多嘅tweet請入bot搵<br />\n<br />\n（twitter戰線)國際都關注今次香港的區選<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754022</a>"},{"pid":"b1ef767aaf70c2bf7ccf4927bd1a87fb77c8a9d7","tid":1754592,"uid":15415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:15:58.000Z","msg":"自推，求下你地真正和勇合一，講乜都假，一齊管錢先係真正齊上齊落，唔好食人血饅頭，一定食唔到兩屆咁耐。"},{"pid":"26330cd53ff270db5d672a354c031177bd191866","tid":1754592,"uid":316537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:17:48.000Z","msg":"其實星火D錢會唔會多過612"},{"pid":"d47c55b2fb0cdce6226bece360650209aafd7979","tid":1754592,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:36:48.000Z","msg":"捐畀星火，612咪得"},{"pid":"53496de689cdb3ce41bfa6288b7593bd19ef5b8d","tid":1754592,"uid":269712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:42:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">新抗爭基金 除左幫義士手足外, 更重要係建立更大嘅黃色經濟圈<br />\n第一  可以俾手足唔再怕冇左份工, 有穩定收入 對持續運動好重要<br />\n第二  更大黃色經濟圈, 更有力同支那對抗 , 同時俾大家睇到改變 更有力量持續運動</span>"},{"pid":"8f4a8421659acd36368bf3ca6a31b8c5da427c7b","tid":1754592,"uid":15415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53496de689cdb3ce41bfa6288b7593bd19ef5b8d","tid":1754592,"uid":269712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:42:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">新抗爭基金 除左幫義士手足外, 更重要係建立更大嘅黃色經濟圈<br />\n第一  可以俾手足唔再怕冇左份工, 有穩定收入 對持續運動好重要<br />\n第二  更大黃色經濟圈, 更有力同支那對抗 , 同時俾大家睇到改變 更有力量持續運動</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:43:58.000Z","msg":"無錯，呢D都係612同星火做唔到"},{"pid":"380b59e25794910692739f77029294bf4b743068","tid":1754592,"uid":15415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d47c55b2fb0cdce6226bece360650209aafd7979","tid":1754592,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:36:48.000Z","msg":"捐畀星火，612咪得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:52:36.000Z","msg":"612管理人全部泛民大台人，前線同本土既手足唔信任612。<br />\n<br />\n星火較被信任但帳目唔公開，律師以外既支援比較地下化。<br />\n<br />\n新既基金首先係有班議員著數先，比少少錢大大個光環。另外就係要真正做到和勇合一齊上齊落，一齊管錢就最實際。"},{"pid":"0c8caecc3d5eb91d4419ac017b58895a13e29ada","tid":1754592,"uid":277296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e368760c97083f8ac99b99f40e657f3516b0483","tid":1754592,"uid":15415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:12:49.000Z","msg":"你地能夠當選，或多或少係食緊人血饅頭，食完做返少少野天公地道，已經無人期望你地肯上前線，以下係香港人好卑微既要求：<br />\n<br />\n請捐出部分薪津幫被捕人士，安家費又好打官司又好，求下你地大恩大德施